&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for an Application Security Researcher to join us. In this critical role, you will assist us in validating our services and environments according to the highest security standards. Also, You will work closely with our R&amp;amp;D and Product teams, and solve complex security problems.&lt;/div&gt;
