&lt;ul class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__bullet&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;unordered-list&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously checking and improving security measures to protect our systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reviewing system architecture, design, and code to find and fix security weaknesses before they become a problem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Helping developers follow secure coding practices and learn how to prevent security risks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Staying updated on new security threats and best practices to keep our security standards high.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Contributing to Cato’s security research blog.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
