&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;At least 3 years of experience in application security or vulnerability research.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Hands-on experience in&amp;nbsp;penetration testing&amp;nbsp;for web, mobile, infrastructure, and&amp;nbsp;thick client&amp;nbsp;applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Experience bypassing security tools like&amp;nbsp;RBI, EDR, and DLP.&lt;/li&gt;
