&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Ability to find and fix security flaws in&amp;nbsp;open-source libraries&amp;nbsp;and third-party software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Knowledge of&amp;nbsp;supply chain attacks&amp;nbsp;and how to prevent them.&lt;/li&gt;
