&lt;li&gt;Be a change agent within Cato Networks, help define new models and processes to grow our business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain highly collaborative relationships with the Presales, Operations, Product, and Customer Success teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make our customers successful!&lt;/li&gt;
