&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;We&#39;re looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Business Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing Business Analytics team. In this role, you&#39;ll partner with &lt;strong&gt;Product, Customer Support, GTM, Finance, and Data/BI&lt;/strong&gt; teams to deliver scalable analytics solutions that drive smarter business decisions across the organization.&lt;br&gt;This is a broad business-facing analytics role, designed to support multiple business domains based on evolving company priorities. You&#39;ll combine analytical thinking, business acumen, and technical expertise to transform data into actionable insights, build scalable reporting solutions, and enable data-driven decision-making across the company.&lt;br&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone with a strong understanding of SaaS business metrics, excellent communication skills, and a passion for leveraging &lt;strong&gt;Generative AI and modern analytics tools&lt;/strong&gt; to improve business processes, automate workflows, and accelerate insight generation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Analytics &amp;amp; Insights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with cross-functional stakeholders to understand business needs and translate them into scalable analytics solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build reports, dashboards, and KPIs that support operational and strategic decision-making across &lt;strong&gt;Product, Customer Support, GTM, Finance&lt;/strong&gt;, and other business functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze business performance, identify trends, risks, and opportunities, and provide actionable recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a deep understanding of business processes and proactively identify opportunities where data and analytics can improve operational efficiency and decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex data into clear business insights and executive-ready presentations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform ad-hoc analyses to support strategic initiatives and business priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data &amp;amp; Analytics Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;strong&gt;SQL&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Snowflake&lt;/strong&gt; to extract, transform, and analyze business data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and maintain end-to-end dashboards using &lt;strong&gt;Tableau&lt;/strong&gt; (preferred) or similar BI visualization tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with &lt;strong&gt;Data Engineering and BI&lt;/strong&gt; teams to improve data models, reporting infrastructure, and data quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage &lt;strong&gt;Generative AI and automation tools&lt;/strong&gt; to improve analytical workflows, accelerate insight generation, and empower business users.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously identify opportunities to improve reporting processes and analytical methodologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
