&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1066&quot; data-end=&quot;1092&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1054&quot; data-end=&quot;1092&quot;&gt;About AI Security at Cato Networks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cato’s AI Security capabilities extend the Cato SASE platform into the AI and SaaS layers, enabling enterprises to securely adopt and govern AI-powered applications and services. AI Security provides real-time visibility, control, and protection across AI-enabled SaaS platforms by addressing modern threats such as identity abuse, data leakage, misconfigurations, insider risk, and unauthorized AI usage.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By integrating AI Security natively into the Cato SASE Cloud, Cato delivers a unified platform that protects users, networks, SaaS applications, and AI services from a single, globally distributed security architecture.&lt;/p&gt;
