&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly organized and proactive Corporate Events Specialist to support the planning and execution of our global events program. Reporting to the Corporate Events Manager, this role will play a critical part in delivering exceptional event experiences across industry conferences, customer events, executive programs, roadshows, and strategic brand activations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is passionate about event management, thrives in a fast-paced environment, and enjoys coordinating multiple projects simultaneously while collaborating with stakeholders across marketing, sales, and operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the planning and execution of global events, including industry conferences, trade shows and regional roadshows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with event logistics, including venue coordination, registration management, shipping, travel arrangements, and onsite support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate event timelines, project plans, and deliverables to ensure deadlines are met.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with managing vendor communications, contracts, purchase orders, and invoices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate event materials, giveaways, signage, booth assets, and promotional items.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support onsite event execution, including booth setup, staff coordination, and issue resolution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support lead management processes and post-event follow-up activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of experience in event marketing, event coordination, corporate events, or related fields.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational and project management skills with exceptional attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage multiple projects simultaneously in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving skills and ability to adapt to changing priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with tools like Salesforce, marketing automation platforms, and partner portals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to travel occasionally to support onsite event execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot; data-en-clipboard=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
