&lt;p&gt;· Provide the customer with ongoing guidance for all product updates and service updates to ensure awareness of any impact to their environment and facilitate implementation of enhancements to drive further value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Coordinate and facilitate ongoing enablement of Cato SASE features and functionality with various customer IT departments and partners&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Facilitate support tickets to ensure proper prioritization and timely resolution of any platform issues&lt;/p&gt;
