&lt;p&gt;· Collaborate with Customer Success team to identify potential account growth opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Foster collaboration with our product, support and engineering teams and provide feedback from the field on features and functionality.&lt;/p&gt;
